properties.sfomuseum:description: Souvenir edition of San Bruno Herald newspaper, titled “San Bruno Herald Recorder - Progress & Coastside Chronicle presents San Bruno’s first annual Aviation Appreciation Week,” May 15 - 21, 1966, with full-spread images of San Francisco International Airport (SFO), including rendering of South Terminal and 1954 opening of Terminal Building; contains various articles, images, and advertisements; 12 pages.
